rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4448fd826612ea3a49085d9442b8693c1b0137","tid":437344,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以當年推「母語教學」搞死香港一批年輕人</blockquote><br />\n用中文讀phy chem bio 嗰d 上到去應該追得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n用中文讀的99%肥英文or英文唔夠分上唔到"},{"pid":"3e6dbce7d951aab51076044dc80941d402cc6a66","tid":437344,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後有班香港人用純粵語打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰班on9仔，香港唔崇英文唔崇國語，靠垃圾廣東話有今日國際城市？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ab23fbc54bcfa7d03a0564e81c31397a9c1d3b","tid":437344,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;中華民國&quot;譯成英文？</blockquote><br />\nRepublic of china"}]}